Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZION吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋  开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思啊  说什么就这样结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会以为  这样就能了事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  别无视我啊  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面  神话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是伯德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  刚刚的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是今天将要解散的虚假家人里的
